\id COL Bible in Fouta-Jalon Pular
\mt1 ЖЃATAKURU PUULUSA HAA E ЖЃE KOLOOSI ЖЃEN
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Immorde e an min Puulusa, mo Alla hoddiri wonugol *sahaabaajo Iisaa Almasiihu on, wondude e oo musiЙ—Й—o men wi'eteeЙ—o Timotee,
\v 2 haa e mon onon, Й“ee musiЙ“Й“e amen humondirЙ“e e *Almasiihu on, gomЙ—inЙ“e wonЙ“e Koloosi, sella-findeeЙ“e. Yo moЖґЖґere e Й“uttu wonan on immorde e Alla Baaba men.
\s1 Fii no Puulusa Jarniri Alla
\p 
\v 3 MeЙ—en duumi e jarnugol Alla, on Ben Iisaa Almasiihu Joomi men on, e nder ko men torantoo on kon.
\v 4 Ko fii men nanii fii ko gomЙ—inЙ—on Iisaa Almasiihu on kon no wowlee, e giggol ngol yiЙ—uЙ—on yimЙ“e Alla Й“en fow ngol,
\v 5 sabu tama'u mo maranaЙ—on on ka kammu, on mo daaluyee goongaajo on andinnoo on fii mun, Й—un ko Kibaaru MoЖґЖґo
\v 6 hewtuЙ—o ka mon on. Ko wano o woni waЙ—irde batte, o laya e aduna on fow non, ko wano non o woni waЙ—irde batte e hakkunde mon gila ЙІande nanuЙ—on anduЙ—on moЖґЖґere Alla nden e nder goonga on,
\v 7 Й“awto Epafaraasi, oo giЙ—o amen e gollidoowo e amen, hewtinde on Й—ii janndeeji. Himo wonani on golloowo sella-findeejo e telen-ma Almasiihu on,
\v 8 awa kadi o Й“anginanii men fii giggol ngol Ruuhu Allaahu on waЙ—i e mon ngol.
\v 9 Ko Й—un waЙ—i, menen kadi, gila ЙІande men humpitii Й—un, meЙ—en duumii e toranagol on Alla, e toragol yo on hebbine gandal fii faale makko on, wondude e kala faamu e hakkil iwruЙ—un e Ruuhu Allaahu on,
\v 10 fii no wuuriron noone no hawrirani JoomiraaЙ—o on, e no welira mo e kala noone, ngurnЙ—an mon Й—an rima kala noone kuuЙ—e moЖґЖґe, Й“eydoЙ—on e andugol Alla,
\v 11 bawgal mangu makko ngun tiiЙ—ina on e kala huunde, fii no woniron Е‹aЙІЙІiiЙ“e e muЙІЙІiiЙ“e,
\v 12 e hoore hiЙ—on jarnira Baabaajo on weltaare, on WawnuЙ—o on heЙ“ugol geЙ“al ka ndondi ndi o marani gomЙ—inЙ“e Й“en ka laamateeri ndaygu,
\v 13 on JattinЙ—o en mbawdi niЙ“e Й—en,\f a \fr 1:13 \ft 1.13 \it В«Mbawdi niЙ“e Й—enВ»\it* Й—un ko doole bone on.\f* o addii en ka laamateeri ЖЃiЙ—Й—o makko yiЙ—aaЙ—o on,
\v 14 on mo heЙ“irЙ—en cottudi wonkii e yaafuyee junuubaaji.
\s1 Fii ЖЃural Iisaa ngal
\p 
\v 15 Ko on ЖЃiЙ—Й—o woni mbaadi Alla mo yi'otaako on, ko kanko woni afo e hoore kala ko tagaa.
\v 16 Ko fii ko e makko kala huunde tagiraa ka kammu e ka hoore leydi, ko yi'otoo e ko yi'otaako, Й—un ko julle laamu e laamuuji e hooreyaagal e bawЙ—e, fow ko e makko tagiraa, e fii makko kadi tagiraa.
\v 17 Ko kanko adii kala huunde, e kala huunde ko e makko woniri.
\v 18 Ko kanko woni hoore Й“andu ndun, Й—un ko *moftal ngal. Ko kanko woni FuЙ—Й—oode nden, e adaaЙ—o immintineede e hakkunde mayЙ“e Й“en, fii no o wonira Arano e Й—i fow.
\v 19 Ko fii welii Alla ka ko woni e Alla kon fow wona e Almasiihu on,
\v 20 e moЖґЖґintinirgol fow e makko kanko tigi, ko woni ka hoore leydi kon e ko woni ka kammu kon, e nder waЙ—ugol Й“uttu rewrude e ЖґiiЖґan makko hibbaaЙ—an Й—an ka hoore *leggal makko altindiraangal.
\p 
\v 21 Onon kadi, Й“ee woЙ—Й—itinooЙ“e Alla e ayЙ“e makko sabu miijooji mon Й—in e kuuЙ—e mon bonЙ—e Й—en,
\v 22 jooni non ko mayde Й“andu makko ndun o moЖґЖґintiniri hakkunde mon e makko, fii no laatoron yeeso makko kanko Alla laaЙ“uЙ“e, Й“e aldaa e ella e Й“e felnaaki,
\v 23 kono non, ko si tawii hiЙ—on duumii e gomЙ—inal ngal, hiЙ—on tabintinaa, ЙІiiЙ“inaa e maggal, hara on woЙ—Й—itaaki tama'u mo heЙ“irЙ—on Kibaaru MoЖґЖґo mo nanuЙ—on on. On Kibaaru feЙІЙІinanaaЙ—o kala tagaaЙ—o ka ley kammu, ko on min Puulusa mi wonti kurkaadu mun.
\s1 Fii no Puulusa Yangorani Moftal ngal
\p 
\v 24 Jooni miЙ—o weltii e nder tampereeji an Й—in fii mon. Ko fii, e an min, mi timminirii Й“andu an ndun ko Е‹akkunoo e tampereeji Almasiihu on, fii Й“andu makko ndun, ndun-le ko moftal ngal.
\v 25 Ko ngal moftal mi wonani kurkaadu, wano Alla nelirimmi non fii feЙІЙІinangol on daaluyee makko on e ko woni e mun kon fow,
\v 26 Й—un ko on gundoo neeЙ“unooЙ—o suuЙ—aade e nder jamaanuuji Й—in fow, kono jooni o feЙІЙІinanaama laaЙ“uЙ“e makko Й“en,
\v 27 Й“en Й“e Alla faalaa andinde ko honЙ—un woni ngalu mangu on gundoo e hakkunde leЖґЖґi Й—in fow. Ko woni on gundoo: Almasiihu on no e mon, ko Й—un woni tama'u mangu ngun.
\v 28 Ko on men woni feЙІЙІinde fii mun e nder hajagol, janna kala neЙ—Й—o e dow faamu timmungu, fii no kala neЙ—Й—o laatora mokobaa e nder humondiral e Almasiihu on.
\v 29 Ko Й—un mi woni gollande, e nder tippirgol e doole makko wonЙ—e gollude e an no tiiЙ—iri Й—en.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Awa, mi faalaa yo on andu ko tippiro hongo mi rondii fii mon, onon e Й“ee Й“e Laa'udiisa e Й“e yi'aali lan haa hande Й“en.
\v 2 ЖЉun ko fii no Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en wakkilora, e no Й“e tamondirira e nder giggol, Й“e heЙ“a kala ko woni e pellital heewungal iwrungal e faamu, fii andugol gundoo Alla on, Й—un ko *Almasiihu on tigi,
\v 3 on mo ngaluuji faamu ngun e gandal ngal fow suuЙ—ii e mun.
\v 4 Ko mi wi'iri Й—un, ko fii wota hay gooto faljinir on yewtereeji welЙ—i.
\v 5 Ko fii, si tawii mi tawdaaka e mon e Й“andu, kono haray miЙ—o wondi e mon ka Й“ernde, miЙ—o weltori yi'ugol nanondiral yaadungal wongal hakkunde mon ngal, e tiiЙ—eendi gomЙ—inal mon ngal e telen-ma Almasiihu on.
\s1 Fii HeЙ“irgol Almasiihu on Ngurndan HeewuЙ—an
\p 
\v 6 Nde tawnoo on jaЙ“ii Iisaa Almasiihu on wona Joomi mon, awa duumee e humagol e makko.
\v 7 Iree Й—aЙ—i mon Й—in e didoodi mon ndin e makko, tabiton e nder gomЙ—inal ngal wano janniraЙ—on non, wonon heewuЙ“e jarnugol.
\p 
\v 8 Reenee, wota hay gooto e mon hiile, nangiree faamu neЙ—Й—anke e Й—ayni meereeji immorde e aadaaji neЙ—Й—anke e mbawdiiji adunayankeeji, Й—i tawata wonaa e Almasiihu on iwri.
\v 9 Ko fii allankaaku Alla ngun fow no e neЙ—Й—ankaaku Almasiihu on,
\v 10 awa kadi on wonii timmuЙ“e e kala huunde e nder yuЙ“Й“ondiral mon e makko, Й—un ko on WonЙ—o yeesoojo kala laamu e kala bawgal.
\v 11 Ko e nder humondiral mon e makko kadi sunniniraЙ—on *sunninannde nde waЙ—iraaka juuЙ—e neЙ—Й—anke, kono hara ko sunninannde nde Almasiihu on waЙ—i nden, Й—un ko Й“oorugol Й“andu junuubankeeru ndun.
\v 12 On surridaama e makko, e nder *looteede maande kisiyee, on immintinidaama e makko sabu ko gomЙ—inЙ—on bawgal Alla ngal kon, on ImmintinЙ—o mo e hakkunde mayЙ“e Й“en.
\v 13 Onon, Й“e tawata maayiino sabu bonnereeji mon e sabu angal sunninegol mon, kanko Alla o wurnitidii on e Almasiihu on. O yaafanike en bonnereeji men Й—in fow.
\v 14 O montii derol ЙІamaale windanoongol e hoore men ngol, ngol ngol tawata yamirooje mun no Е‹annani en, o ittiri ngol fempugol ngol ka *leggal altindiraangal.
\v 15 O Й“oorii laamuuji Й—in e bawЙ—e Й—en, o weeЙ“itii Й—e e kene e yeeso fow e nder foolirgol Й—e leggal altindiraangal ngal.
\p 
\v 16 Awa ko Й—un waЙ—i, wota gooto ЙІaawu on fii ko ЙІaamoton kon e ko yaroton kon, maa fii juldeere, maa lewru heyru, maa ЙІalaaЙ—e fowteteeЙ—e e mun Й—en.
\v 17 ЖЉun fow ko Й—owdi piiji aroyayЙ—i Й—in, kono haqiiqa on ko Й—i Almasiihu on Й—in.
\v 18 Wota on jaЙ“u Й“en yimЙ“e yiЙ—uЙ“e yankinorde tampingol Й“andu ndun e rewugol malaa'ika hippoo on mbuuЙІaari mon ndin. Sifa Й“en yimЙ“e ko hoolorЙ“e koyЙ—i mun. HiЙ“e hebbinora mawnintinaare nde alaa nafa, immorde e miijooji neЙ—Й—anke,
\v 19 edii Й“e humaade e Hooreejo on, on mo Й“andu ndun fow jogondiriri sabu mun, fottiri jokke Й—en e Й—aЙ—i Й—in, mawni no Alla yiЙ—iri non.
\s1 Fii Wuurugol e nder Humondiral e Almasiihu on
\p 
\v 20 Nde tawnoo on maayidiino e Almasiihu on, on sertii e Й—ii mbawdiiji adunayankeeji, ko honЙ—un jaЙ“anton Й“e fawa on Й—ii aadaaji, wa si tawii hiЙ—on wuurani aduna,
\v 21 Й—un ko В«wota a meemu Й—unЙ—oo!В», В«wota a mettu Й—unЙ—aa!В», В«wota a foppo Й—untoo!В»
\v 22 ЖЉii aadaaji fow si huutoraama ko Й—i bontayЙ—i, Й“ay ko Й—i yamirooje e janndeeji neЙ—Й—anke.
\v 23 Pellet, ko goonga, Й—in aadaaji no nandi e faamu, Й“ay hiЙ—i catii e dewal anniyaangal immorde e neЙ—Й—anke, e yankinaare e yangugol Й“andu, kono Й—i alanaa neЙ—Й—anke no o wawtora hoore makko.
\c 3
\s1 Fii ЖЃooragol KuuЙ—e BonЙ—e Й—en, ЖЃornoo KuuЙ—e MoЖґЖґe Й—en
\p 
\v 1 ЖЃay non on wurnitidaama e *Almasiihu on, haray Й—aЙ“Й“ee piiji wonЙ—i ka dow Й—in, ka Almasiihu on jooЙ—ori ka sengo ЙІaamo Alla ton.
\v 2 Miijee fii ko woni ka dow kon, hara hinaa fii ko woni ka hoore leydi kon.
\v 3 Ko fii on maayii, ngurndan mon Й—an no suuЙ—ii e Almasiihu on ka Alla.
\v 4 Awa, nde Almasiihu on, Й—un ko ngurndan mon Й—an, feeЙІiti, haray on feeЙІiday e makko ka mangural.
\p 
\v 5 Awa waree piiji adunayankeeji wonЙ—i e mon Й—in, Й—un ko wano: jinaa e angal laaЙ“al e himmeeji e faaleeji bonЙ—i e miile, (ko fii miile ko rewugol sanamu).
\v 6 Ko Й—un addata tikkere Alla nden e hoore murtuЙ“e Й“en.
\v 7 Ko nii wuurirnoЙ—on oya tuma, wa fewndo junuubu ardinoo ngurndan mon Й—an.
\v 8 Kono jooni non, onon kadi bugitee Й—un fow: Й—un ko tikkere nden e monee on e hunЖґeendi ndin e hoyre nden e haalaaji bonЙ—i yaltaynooЙ—i e kundule mon Й—in.
\v 9 Wota on fenindiran, onon Й“ee Й“ortiiЙ“e tagu hinngu ngun e kuuЙ—e mun,
\v 10 Й“ornii tagu hesu heyЙ—intinaangu e noone mbaadi on TaguЙ—o ngu, fii no waawiron mo andude haa timma.
\v 11 ЖЉon alaa *Gereekiyankeejo maa *Yahuudiyankeejo, maa sunninaaЙ—o maa mo sunninaaka, maa leЙІol ngol finaa maa leЙІol kaana-jikkuwol, maa maccuЙ—o maa dimo, kono ko Almasiihu on woni fow, woni e fow.
\p 
\v 12 ЖЃay ko on suЙ“aaЙ“e Alla, laaЙ“uЙ“e, e yiЙ—aaЙ“e makko, Й“ornee yurmeende tiiЙ—unde e moЖґЖґuki e yankinaare e newaare e yondinaare.
\v 13 MuЙІЙІondiranee, yaafondiron si tawii goЙ—Й—o no mari ko wullitoo e hoore oya. Wano Almasiihu on yaaforani on non, onon kadi waЙ—iree wano non.
\v 14 Kono, e hoore Й—unЙ—oo fow, Й“ornee giggol, sabu ko ngol yuЙ“Й“indirta haa timma.
\v 15 Yo Й“uttu Almasiihu ngu noddiraЙ—on fii wonugol Й“andu wooturu ngun ardo Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en. Wonee anditanooЙ“e.
\v 16 Yo kongol Almasiihu on hebbin Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en. Jannindiree, hajondiron e dow faamu fow e nder ko beytiranton Alla beyti Zabuura e jaarooje e beyti hormorЙ—i, yettiron Alla beytirangol mo Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en fow.
\v 17 Kala ko waЙ—oton, e kongol maa e kuugal, waЙ—ee fow e innde Iisaa Joomi on, e jarnirgol mo Alla Baabaajo on.
\s1 Fii no ЖЃeynguure AlmasiiyaaЙ“e Haani Wonirde
\p 
\v 18 RewЙ“e, mo kala e mon, yo yankinano moodi mun, wano hawrirani JoomiraaЙ—o on non.
\v 19 Onon kadi worЙ“e, mo kala e mon yo yiЙ—u Й“eyngu mun, hara on hunЖґanaali Й“e.
\p 
\v 20 Onon kadi fayЙ“e, Й—oftee mawЙ“e mon Й“en e Й—i fow, ko fii Й—un no wela JoomiraaЙ—o on.
\v 21 Onon kadi baabiraaЙ“e, wota on mettin Й“erЙ—e fayЙ“e mon Й“en, fii wota Й“erЙ—e maЙ“Й“e maayu.
\p 
\v 22 Onon kadi yo jiyaaЙ“e, Й—oftee jeyЙ“e on jeyal adunayankewal Й“en e Й—i fow, hara hinaa non e gite maЙ“Й“e tun, wa si tawii on Й—aЙ“Й“ay woni no yimЙ“e Й“en yiЙ—ira on, kono hara ko Й“ernde laaЙ“unde e nder kulol JoomiraaЙ—o on.
\v 23 Kala ko waЙ—oton, waЙ—iree Й—un ittiri wonkii mon kin fow, wa si tawii ko JoomiraaЙ—o on wonЙ—on waЙ—ande, hara hinaa yimЙ“e Й“en,
\v 24 e hoore andugol mon on heЙ“iray JoomiraaЙ—o on ndondi wa ngeenaari. Ko Almasiihu Joomi on wonЙ—on kurkanaade.
\v 25 Ko fii kala on waЙ—uЙ—o ko boni, o hettay njoddi bonnere makko nden, awa kadi giЙ—aale alaa ton.
\c 4
\p 
\v 1 Onon kadi yo jeyЙ“e, jogoree jiyaaЙ“e mon Й“en no feewiri e no nunЙ—iri, e hoore andugol wonde onon kadi hiЙ—on mari JeyЙ—o on ka kammu.
\s1 Fii Waajuuji Puulusa Goo
\p 
\v 2 Duumee e toragol Alla, hakkilanon e Й—un e dow yettugol mo.
\v 3 ToranoЙ—on men kadi, fii yo Alla udditan konguЙ—i amen Й—in dambugal fii no men waawira feЙІЙІinirde goonga lugguЙ—o *Almasiihu on, on goonga mo mi jolkaa fii mun,
\v 4 e no mi yewtira fii on goonga no laaЙ“iri, wano haaniranimmi non.
\v 5 E telen-ma Й“e gomЙ—inaa Й“en, wondiree faamu, hara on accaali fajuhun woo feЖґЖґira on.
\v 6 Yo taw soono woo konguЙ—i mon Й—in ko welЙ—i, hara hiЙ—i weliri wa lanЙ—an, fii no andiron ko honno jaaborton mo kala.
\s1 Fii Rawnoode nden e Salminaango ngon
\p 
\v 7 Tikiiki, oo musiЙ—Й—o an yiЙ—aaЙ—o, golloowo holniiЙ—o mo mi kurkodata fii golle JoomiraaЙ—o on, o andinoyay on fow fii no mi fewndori.
\v 8 Ko waЙ—i si mi immini mo haa e mon, ko fii no andiron no men fewndori, e fii yo o wakkilin Й“erЙ—e mon Й—en.
\v 9 Mi immindinanii on mo e oo musiЙ—Й—o yiЙ—aaЙ—o sella-findeejo wi'eteeЙ—o Onesiima, on ko mo mon. ЖЃe andinoyay on ko woni feЖґЖґude gaa kon fow.
\p 
\v 10 Oo wondiЙ—Й—o an e joge wi'eteeЙ—o Aristarke salminii on, wondude e Markuusa, oo denЙ—iraawo Barnabaasi, on mo tindinanaЙ—on fii mun. Si o hewtoyii ka mon, wernee mo moЖґЖґa.
\v 11 Iisaa jammaaЙ—o Yustuusa kadi salminii on. E nder leЙІol *Yahuuda ngol, ko Й“ee Й—oo tun woni gollidude e an fii *laamateeri Alla ndin, Й“e woni wakkilinЙ“e lan.
\v 12 Oo kurkaadu Iisaa Almasiihu on wi'eteeЙ—o Epafaraasi salminii on, on ko mo mon. Himo duumii e tippiro fii mon e nder torndeeji makko Й—in, fii no tabitiron wa mokobaaЙ“e, heewuЙ“e hoolaare e telen-ma faale Alla on fow.
\v 13 MiЙ—o seeditanii mo Й—un, wonde o yanganike on fota, e fii Й“ee Й“e Laa'udiisa e fii Й“ee Й“e Hiirapoliisa.
\p 
\v 14 Awa kadi, oo ЙІawndoowo yiЙ—aaЙ—o wi'eteeЙ—o Luuka, wondude e Demaasi, salminii on.
\v 15 Salminanee lan musiЙ“Й“e wonЙ“e Laa'udiisa Й“en, kaЙІun e oo debbo wi'eteeЙ—o Nimfaasi, e *moftal wongal ka suudu makko ngal.
\v 16 Si nduu Й“atakuru jangaama ka mon, etee kadi no ndu jangiree ka moftal wongal Laa'udiisa. Jangon kadi iwranayndu on ndun Laa'udiisa.
\v 17 Wi'on kadi oo wi'eteeЙ—o Arkiipe yo o eto no o timminira Й—ee golle Й—e o heЙ“iri JoomiraaЙ—o on.
\p 
\v 18 Min Puulusa, mi salminirii on jungo an ngon tigi. Awa anditee fii jolokooje an Й—en. Yo moЖґЖґere wonan on.
